[I am concerned that the comment above has not taken into
consideration the implication of capture/endoscopic examination of
these sensitive and wild birds. While the writer indicates a more
sensitive way to access disease, the logistics of this manipulation
in wild birds deserves caution. Though the approach undertaken by the
authors of the discussed paper may, perhaps, not be optimal, it may
be more logically feasible. - Mod.TG]
